reviewText: He is a crack up!!!! We love hearing his warped sense of humor, he is great!!!! Very talented!! Would and do tell everyone we know to look him up!!

We already had his hilarious Greatest Hits Vol. 2 and were really looking forward to this one being as funny, but it didn't even come close. We didn't even finish watching it.
Would not recommend this video.

My wife is from Maine, and we are always interested in MAINE humor. Bob Marley, however is just like every other foul mouthed comedian on the circuit.  AFter a while, it was just embarassing to listen to him and I'm certainly not a prude being a 20+ year military retiree.
John Dorgan
